00:40:24,010 --> 00:40:26,010
Your Highness, these are for you.

815
00:40:29,930 --> 00:40:30,930
Congratulations

816
00:40:31,210 --> 00:40:33,400
on overcoming yourself
in front of everyone

817
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:34,660
and proving yourself.

818
00:40:35,030 --> 00:40:35,760
Thank you.

819
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,630
I also feel

820
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:40,130
that something within me has changed.

821
00:40:42,460 --> 00:40:44,830
My Lord, as per your instructions,

822
00:40:45,070 --> 00:40:46,870
the refugees have been settled.

823
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:49,280
However, Wayun still needs to be repaired.

824
00:40:50,670 --> 00:40:51,960
This is the budget I obtained

825
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:52,790
from the Ministry
of Government Supervision

826
00:40:52,790 --> 00:40:54,960
and the allocation records from that time.

827
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:56,550
There's a huge discrepancy.

828
00:40:56,550 --> 00:40:57,480
I suspect

829
00:40:57,500 --> 00:40:59,230
that there must be corruption.

830
00:41:02,030 --> 00:41:03,100
But you can't

831
00:41:03,120 --> 00:41:05,250
find anything in the accounts, right?

832
00:41:05,260 --> 00:41:07,390
It's because all the key personnel
are dead.

833
00:41:07,390 --> 00:41:08,790
We can't trace anything.

834
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:16,540
I originally wanted to bring this matter
to light

835
00:41:16,540 --> 00:41:18,250
and force the real culprits to come out

836
00:41:18,250 --> 00:41:20,380
to solve the issue of Wayun's repairs.

837
00:41:20,550 --> 00:41:22,960
But those old foxes
at the Three Central Offices

838
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:24,670
turned it right back on us,

839
00:41:24,850 --> 00:41:26,310
pushing the problem back.

840
00:41:27,550 --> 00:41:30,360
It seems I've underestimated
the complexity of the situation.

841
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:32,510
My Lord, what should we do now?

842
00:41:32,690 --> 00:41:33,690
Form an alliance.

843
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:51,810
I, Luo Minghai, never indulge in alcohol,

844
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:53,900
and I certainly won't drink with you.

845
00:41:53,910 --> 00:41:54,540
I know.

846
00:41:58,920 --> 00:42:00,580
But I have a favor to ask of you.

847
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,900
This is proper etiquette.

848
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:13,880
You think I would agree to help you,
the Executioner on the Battlefield,

849
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:15,490
who kills without mercy?

850
00:42:15,630 --> 00:42:17,730
Now that corruption is rampant these days

851
00:42:17,730 --> 00:42:20,260
and the refugee issue
has caused quite a stir,

852
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:23,740
not everyone dares to investigate
the Three Central Offices.

853
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:30,230
If I join forces with
the Three Central Offices,

854
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:32,030
won't you be asking for trouble?

855
00:42:32,250 --> 00:42:32,930
Lord Luo.

856
00:42:34,710 --> 00:42:37,680
I believe that, as the Commander-in-Chief
of the Ministry of War,

857
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:39,320
you absolutely wouldn't do such a thing.

858
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,600
If this case succeeds,

859
00:42:41,190 --> 00:42:45,440
your ministry will take the credit
and enjoy the rewards effortlessly.

860
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:47,540
Although we have old grudges,

861
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:50,580
we also understand each other
very well, right?

862
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:52,880
So, you should know that I, Di Lin,

863
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:54,360
never seek credit for myself.

864
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:56,390
As long as we uncover who's behind this,

865
00:42:56,390 --> 00:42:57,410
all the credit

866
00:42:57,990 --> 00:42:59,580
will be yours, Lord Luo.

867
00:43:01,140 --> 00:43:02,330
If it fails,

868
00:43:02,820 --> 00:43:04,440
and we offend
the Three Central Offices,

869
00:43:04,440 --> 00:43:05,880
then my ministry will be in trouble.

870
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:07,030
If it fails,

871
00:43:07,240 --> 00:43:10,480
my Ministry of Military and Legal Affairs
will bear all the consequences.

872
00:43:10,480 --> 00:43:14,590
Alright. I agree to collaborate with you.

873
00:43:14,910 --> 00:43:15,540
But

874
00:43:16,450 --> 00:43:18,870
all the evidence you've found

875
00:43:19,230 --> 00:43:21,100
must be shared with my ministry.

876
00:43:21,530 --> 00:43:22,340
No problem.

877
00:43:25,890 --> 00:43:28,410
I knew you cared deeply about Zichuan

878
00:43:28,700 --> 00:43:30,360
and would never stand by idly.

879
00:43:33,240 --> 00:43:35,150
I won't take your wine.

880
00:43:40,110 --> 00:43:41,570
Let's keep it here for now.

881
00:43:42,550 --> 00:43:43,840
I believe that one day,

882
00:43:44,230 --> 00:43:46,250
you'll drink with me willingly.
